<subSubSection id="D165C460071510515E32A83E6252FBD5" pageId="0" pageNumber="52779" type="description">
<paragraph id="595CB5EB477EAFC9A8B3895960B66A46" pageId="0" pageNumber="52779">Description</paragraph>
<paragraph id="F91D8E20AFE9A11695DF85424386F6A5" pageId="0" pageNumber="52779">
Morphological characters of the voucher specimen from Son La Province agreed well with the descriptions of 
<bibRefCitation id="196D09C83EBAD88A1349DBE83839A313" author="Orlov, N L" journalOrPublisher="Russian Journal of Herpetology" pageId="0" pageNumber="52779" pagination="181 - 197" refId="B5672371" refString="Orlov, N L, Ryabov, S A, 2004. Revalidization and change of taxonomic status of Dinodon rufozonatum meridionale Bourret, 1935 (Serpentes: Colubridae: Colubrinae). Russian Journal of Herpetology 11 (3): 181 - 197" title="Revalidization and change of taxonomic status of Dinodon rufozonatum meridionale Bourret, 1935 (Serpentes: Colubridae: Colubrinae)" volume="11" year="2004">Orlov and Ryabov (2004)</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="04A3DC9140F44BCF4EB60A88FB2C7FCB" author="Hecht, V L" journalOrPublisher="Biodiversity Journal" pageId="0" pageNumber="52779" pagination="507 - 552" refId="B5672226" refString="Hecht, V L, Pham, C T, Nguyen, T T, Nguyen, T Q, Bonkowski, M, Ziegler, T, 2013. First report on the herpetofauna of Tay Yen Tu Nature Reserve, northeastern Vietnam. Biodiversity Journal 4: 507 - 552" title="First report on the herpetofauna of Tay Yen Tu Nature Reserve, northeastern Vietnam." volume="4" year="2013">Hecht et al. (2013)</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="59CA2D1CBAC9C89C8D2478B33728EA2A" author="Nguyen, T V" journalOrPublisher="Tap chi Sinh hoc (Journal of Biology)" pageId="0" pageNumber="52779" pagination="324 - 332" refId="B5672340" refString="Nguyen, T V, Pham, C T, Nguyen, T Q, 2016. New records and an updated list of snakes (Squamata: Serpentes) from Xuan Lien Nature Reserve, Thanh Hoa Province, Vietnam. Tap chi Sinh hoc (Journal of Biology) 38 (3): 324 - 332" title="New records and an updated list of snakes (Squamata: Serpentes) from Xuan Lien Nature Reserve, Thanh Hoa Province, Vietnam" volume="38" year="2016">Nguyen et al. (2016)</bibRefCitation>
and 
<bibRefCitation id="CEC695DE7E120279887365F0843488D0" author="Nguyen, T Q" journalOrPublisher="Bonn Zoological Bulletin" pageId="0" pageNumber="52779" pagination="15 - 24" refId="B5672329" refString="Nguyen, T Q, Nguyen, T V, Pham, C T, Ong, A V, Ziegler, T, 2018. New records of snakes (Squamata: Serpentes) from Hoa Binh Province, northwestern Vietnam. Bonn Zoological Bulletin 67 (1): 15 - 24" title="New records of snakes (Squamata: Serpentes) from Hoa Binh Province, northwestern Vietnam" volume="67" year="2018">Nguyen et al. (2018)</bibRefCitation>
: SVL 810 mm, TaL 227 mm (n = 1); head distinct from neck; internasals not in contact with loreal; nasal divided; loreal 1/1, not touching the eye; preocular 1/1; subocular absent; postoculars 2/2; anterior temporals 2/3, posterior temporals 3/3; supralabials 8/8, third to fifth entering orbit; infralabials 10/10; dorsal scale rows 17-17-15, strongly keeled except 5 outermost rows smooth, outer dorsal scales enlarged; ventrals 250 (+ 2 preventrals); cloacal undivided; subcaudals 104, divided.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="6D8F66FA62CEA2A0F65D165F61762EFF" pageId="0" pageNumber="52779">
Colouration in life: dorsal surface black, with 122 narrow yellow cross-bars on body and 35 on tail, bifurcated on the sides, enclosing dark spots; head dark black with symmetrical light markings, the most conspicuous being the one running from the eye to the margin of the snout and another stretching from the hind margin of the parietals; belly cream; lower surface of tail dark brown (Fig. 
<figureCitation id="2FBD6BB6BEFDB55BC6A8E6FF831325B5" captionStart="Figure 4" captionStartId="F5672581" captionText="Figure 4. Lycodon meridionalis (TBU SL. 2016. 144, adult female) from Son La Province, Vietnam. Photo: N. B. Sung" figureDoi="10.3897/BDJ.8.e52779.figure4" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/395547" pageId="0" pageNumber="52779">4</figureCitation>
).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="3B078430CC752864B9B3A480324FF52D" pageId="0" pageNumber="52779" type="distribution">
<paragraph id="0864FA6824932E212BD639AF4B6CADB4" pageId="0" pageNumber="52779">Distribution</paragraph>
<paragraph id="6EEA97DBDACA41CB55368CFC99EEDB15" pageId="0" pageNumber="52779">
In Vietnam, this species has been reported from Lao Cai and Ha Giang provinces in the north, southwards to Thanh Hoa Province (
<bibRefCitation id="E2B42727088738CCC8F62E9DF15AC1F9" author="Nguyen, S V" journalOrPublisher="Edition Chimaira, Frankfurt am Main" pageId="0" pageNumber="52779" refId="B5672320" refString="Nguyen, S V, Ho, C T, Nguyen, T Q, 2009. Herpetofauna of Vietnam. Edition Chimaira, Frankfurt am Main" title="Herpetofauna of Vietnam" year="2009">Nguyen et al. 2009</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="374A3B94CDEF45F5B1F44B49658E42FE" author="Ziegler, T" journalOrPublisher="Herpetology Notes" pageId="0" pageNumber="52779" pagination="185 - 201" refId="B5672539" refString="Ziegler, T, Tran, D T A, Nguyen, T Q, Perl, R G B, Wirk, L, Kulisch, M, Lehmann, T, Anna, R, Nguyen, T T, Le, Q K, Vu, T N, 2014. New amphibian and reptile records from Ha Giang Province, northern Vietnam. Herpetology Notes 7: 185 - 201" title="New amphibian and reptile records from Ha Giang Province, northern Vietnam" volume="7" year="2014">Ziegler et al. 2014</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="DC6ECE66E4571350267A319E7345C36C" author="Nguyen, T Q" journalOrPublisher="Bonn Zoological Bulletin" pageId="0" pageNumber="52779" pagination="15 - 24" refId="B5672329" refString="Nguyen, T Q, Nguyen, T V, Pham, C T, Ong, A V, Ziegler, T, 2018. New records of snakes (Squamata: Serpentes) from Hoa Binh Province, northwestern Vietnam. Bonn Zoological Bulletin 67 (1): 15 - 24" title="New records of snakes (Squamata: Serpentes) from Hoa Binh Province, northwestern Vietnam" volume="67" year="2018">Nguyen et al. 2018</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="DB3A804BE09B1FA8EF8C9A98BE6CC7BE" author="Nguyen, T V" journalOrPublisher="Tap chi Sinh hoc (Journal of Biology)" pageId="0" pageNumber="52779" pagination="324 - 332" refId="B5672340" refString="Nguyen, T V, Pham, C T, Nguyen, T Q, 2016. New records and an updated list of snakes (Squamata: Serpentes) from Xuan Lien Nature Reserve, Thanh Hoa Province, Vietnam. Tap chi Sinh hoc (Journal of Biology) 38 (3): 324 - 332" title="New records and an updated list of snakes (Squamata: Serpentes) from Xuan Lien Nature Reserve, Thanh Hoa Province, Vietnam" volume="38" year="2016">Nguyen et al. 2016</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="D0F913672C995D104BBECFBD49508074" author="Nguyen, T Q" journalOrPublisher="Bonn Zoological Bulletin" pageId="0" pageNumber="52779" pagination="15 - 24" refId="B5672329" refString="Nguyen, T Q, Nguyen, T V, Pham, C T, Ong, A V, Ziegler, T, 2018. New records of snakes (Squamata: Serpentes) from Hoa Binh Province, northwestern Vietnam. Bonn Zoological Bulletin 67 (1): 15 - 24" title="New records of snakes (Squamata: Serpentes) from Hoa Binh Province, northwestern Vietnam" volume="67" year="2018">Nguyen et al. 2018</bibRefCitation>
). Elsewhere, the species has been reported from China and Laos (
<bibRefCitation id="C42500BB907BA60788BDBBDEACDA65DD" author="Nguyen, S V" journalOrPublisher="Edition Chimaira, Frankfurt am Main" pageId="0" pageNumber="52779" refId="B5672320" refString="Nguyen, S V, Ho, C T, Nguyen, T Q, 2009. Herpetofauna of Vietnam. Edition Chimaira, Frankfurt am Main" title="Herpetofauna of Vietnam" year="2009">Nguyen et al. 2009</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="F773E1E6DDA4FF06C9F2ED92E75423C7" author="Ziegler, T" journalOrPublisher="Herpetology Notes" pageId="0" pageNumber="52779" pagination="185 - 201" refId="B5672539" refString="Ziegler, T, Tran, D T A, Nguyen, T Q, Perl, R G B, Wirk, L, Kulisch, M, Lehmann, T, Anna, R, Nguyen, T T, Le, Q K, Vu, T N, 2014. New amphibian and reptile records from Ha Giang Province, northern Vietnam. Herpetology Notes 7: 185 - 201" title="New amphibian and reptile records from Ha Giang Province, northern Vietnam" volume="7" year="2014">Ziegler et al. 2014</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="CDDBC68EEE58C280F5EB94C3CC6C824C" author="Nguyen, T V" journalOrPublisher="Tap chi Sinh hoc (Journal of Biology)" pageId="0" pageNumber="52779" pagination="324 - 332" refId="B5672340" refString="Nguyen, T V, Pham, C T, Nguyen, T Q, 2016. New records and an updated list of snakes (Squamata: Serpentes) from Xuan Lien Nature Reserve, Thanh Hoa Province, Vietnam. Tap chi Sinh hoc (Journal of Biology) 38 (3): 324 - 332" title="New records and an updated list of snakes (Squamata: Serpentes) from Xuan Lien Nature Reserve, Thanh Hoa Province, Vietnam" volume="38" year="2016">Nguyen et al. 2016</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="69FB72E6B680C5BE8F758F05FE79AD33" author="Nguyen, T Q" journalOrPublisher="Bonn Zoological Bulletin" pageId="0" pageNumber="52779" pagination="15 - 24" refId="B5672329" refString="Nguyen, T Q, Nguyen, T V, Pham, C T, Ong, A V, Ziegler, T, 2018. New records of snakes (Squamata: Serpentes) from Hoa Binh Province, northwestern Vietnam. Bonn Zoological Bulletin 67 (1): 15 - 24" title="New records of snakes (Squamata: Serpentes) from Hoa Binh Province, northwestern Vietnam" volume="67" year="2018">Nguyen et al. 2018</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="F252F31A93193D09328FA8769E33378B" pageId="0" pageNumber="52779" type="ecology">
<paragraph id="4B25E5A65F35A61388A151748B5B7D79" pageId="0" pageNumber="52779">Ecology</paragraph>
<paragraph id="A6175CCC169B479ACAA22B632611926B" pageId="0" pageNumber="52779">The voucher specimen was found at 09:10 h on the ground. The surrounding habitat was secondary forest composed of medium and small hardwoods, lianes and shrub. Air temperature was 27-32°C and relative humidity was 65-70%.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
